---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Self-Hosted Coolify"
  canonicalUrl="https://coolify.io/self-hosted/"
  description="Self-host with Coolify for full control, no hidden costs, and unlimited resources. Open-source with all features included."
>
  <h1
    class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white md:text-6xl px-4"
  >
    Why should you self-host<span class="text-warning">?</span>
  </h1>
  <h2 class="text-base pb-10 pt-2 text-neutral-400 px-4">You will be cool.</h2>
  <div class="pb-2 flex justify-center text-center gap-8 px-4">
    <a
      href="https://coolify.io/docs/installation"
      class="text-base font-bold rounded p-4 px-10 text-white bg-coolgray-300 hover:bg-coolgray-400 flex gap-2 w-64 justify-center"
      ><i class="ph-duotone ph-rocket-launch text-warning text-xl" aria-hidden="true"></i>Get Started</a
    >
  </div>
  <div class="space-y-2 pt-10">
    <div
      class="tracking-tight text-white font-mono bg-coolgray-300 px-4 py-2 rounded text-xs md:text-sm text-left w-fit space-y-1 mx-auto"
    >
      <div class="select-none text-neutral-400 fontfont-bold pr-2 pb-4">
        # The self-hosted version is ready on your server in under a minute - <span
          class="text-warning/90">always free, with all functionalities</span
        >.
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
        <div>
          <span class="select-none text-neutral-500 font-extrabold pr-2">></span
          >curl -fsSL https://cdn.coollabs.io/coolify/install.sh | sudo bash
        </div>
        <button
          id="copy-btn"
          class="text-neutral-400 hover:text-white transition-colors flex-shrink-0"
          aria-label="Copy command"
        >
          <i class="ph-duotone ph-clipboard text-xl" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <h3
    class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white md:text-3xl pt-10 px-4"
  >
    Self-hosting in general<span class="text-warning">.</span>
  </h3>
  <h4 class="text-base pb-10 pt-2 text-neutral-400 px-4">
    There are plenty of benefits.
  </h4>
  <div class="mt-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto px-2">
    <ul role="list" class="mt-8 space-y-8 text-neutral-400 text-left">
      <li class="flex gap-x-3">
        <i class="ph-duotone ph-check-circle mt-0 flex-none text-warning text-2xl" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <span
          ><strong class="font-semibold text-warning">No Hidden Costs.</strong> Cloud
          providers can become costly once you surpass the free tier. Once you go
          beyond the free tier, expenses can accumulate rapidly. There are plenty
          of <a
            class="underline text-white"
            href="https://serverlesshorrors.com/?utm_source=coolify.io"
            target="_blank">horror stories</a
          >.
        </span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-x-3">
        <i class="ph-duotone ph-check-circle mt-0 flex-none text-warning text-2xl" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <span
          ><strong class="font-semibold text-warning">Cost Efficient.</strong> You
          get way more resources for your money and you can save a lot (thousands
          of $) every month, like <a
            class="underline text-white"
            href="https://twitter.com/heyandras/status/1742078215986860460"
            target="_blank">this</a
          > and <a
            class="underline text-white"
            href="https://twitter.com/heyandras/status/1752209429276086688"
            target="_blank">this</a
          > and <a
            class="underline text-white"
            href="https://twitter.com/heyandras/status/1724510876256944244"
            target="_blank">this</a
          >.
        </span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-x-3">
        <i class="ph-duotone ph-check-circle mt-0 flex-none text-warning text-2xl" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <span
          ><strong class="font-semibold text-warning"
            >Easier Than You Think.</strong
          > Servers (hardware + software) have changed a lot since cloud providers
          emerged. And with software (like <a
            href="/"
            class="text-white underline">Coolify</a
          >), you can start hosting in minutes without any maintenance work.
        </span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-x-3">
        <i class="ph-duotone ph-check-circle mt-0 flex-none text-warning text-2xl" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <span
          ><strong class="font-semibold text-warning">Data Privacy.</strong> Currently,
          data privacy is a major issue. By self-hosting, you have complete control
          over your data and can guarantee that it is not being misused.
        </span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <h3
    class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white md:text-3xl pt-10 px-4"
  >
    Self-hosting with Coolify<span class="text-warning">.</span>
  </h3>
  <h4 class="text-base pb-10 pt-2 text-neutral-400 px-4">
    Even more benefits.
  </h4>
  <div class="mt-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto px-2">
    <ul role="list" class="mt-8 space-y-8 text-neutral-400 text-left">
      <li class="flex gap-x-3">
        <i class="ph-duotone ph-check-circle mt-0 flex-none text-warning text-2xl" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <span
          ><strong class="font-semibold text-warning"
            >No Features Behind Paywall.</strong
          > Everything is included in the open-source software (OSS) version. And
          will always be.
        </span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-x-3">
        <i class="ph-duotone ph-check-circle mt-0 flex-none text-warning text-2xl" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <span
          ><strong class="font-semibold text-warning">No Limitations.</strong> You
          have the freedom to host an unlimited number of websites on any quantity
          of servers without any restrictions.
        </span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-x-3">
        <i class="ph-duotone ph-check-circle mt-0 flex-none text-warning text-2xl" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <span
          ><strong class="font-semibold text-warning">Nice UI.</strong> You get a
          simple and easy to use UI to manage your servers and applications.
        </span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-x-3">
        <i class="ph-duotone ph-check-circle mt-0 flex-none text-warning text-2xl" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <span
          ><strong class="font-semibold text-warning">Open Source.</strong> You can
          see the source code and contribute to it, if you want. You can shape the
          future of the software.
        </span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</Layout>

<script>
  document.getElementById("copy-btn")?.addEventListener("click", () => {
    navigator.clipboard.writeText(
      "curl -fsSL https://cdn.coollabs.io/coolify/install.sh | sudo bash",
    );
    const btn = document.getElementById("copy-btn");
    if (btn) {
      btn.innerHTML = `<i class="ph-duotone ph-check text-xl" aria-hidden="true"></i>`;
      setTimeout(() => {
        btn.innerHTML = `<i class="ph-duotone ph-clipboard text-xl" aria-hidden="true"></i>`;
      }, 2000);
    }
  });
</script>
